Blackjack engine is taken from https://github.com/kedoska/engine-blackjack
Modified to be used for your game, but basics still the same.

Everything in blackjack/engine folder (EXCEPT for deck.js) is from that repo (with minor modifications),
so if you need any info on how things work, visit the link above.

blackjack/engine/deck.js is 52 cards deck generator from https://github.com/kedoska/52-deck/